<br />\n我覺得買一手樓，<br />\naa係無咩用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌，真係笑撚死我，係度講埋d阿媽係女人既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"井底蛙你真係笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b85468a7d515a30ac762c2c7cf8af43c803c1c1","tid":711303,"uid":163248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"講真，agent一定有用<br />\n但值唔值呢個價就好難講<br />\n之前冇咁多網站app，agent係必要，因佢地食左個information asymmetry<br />\n好似傳統銀行咁你有閒錢都唔知邊個想借錢，你就焗存錢去銀行，銀行再借出去食利率差價<br />\n宜家銀行同agent都有同一個挑戰，就係&quot;去中介化&quot;<br />\n有P2P想replace銀行，有網站app想replace地產中介<br />\n銀行就難replace，因佢除左做中介仲有好多作用同業務<br />\n地產agent作用就相對單一<br />\n個人認為地產agent會漸漸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6769d72d384d845c7cef4b5ae442624b3b9faa6c","tid":711303,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"agent遲早會俾ai取代"},{"pid":"d2dcdf0e3e1af932db6eebbc03c69d67e13025a0","tid":711303,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b85468a7d515a30ac762c2c7cf8af43c803c1c1","tid":711303,"uid":163248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"講真，agent一定有用<br />\n但值唔值呢個價就好難講<br />\n之前冇咁多網站app，agent係必要，因佢地食左個information asymmetry<br />\n好似傳統銀行咁你有閒錢都唔知邊個想借錢，你就焗存錢去銀行，銀行再借出去食利率差價<br />\n宜家銀行同agent都有同一個挑戰，就係&quot;去中介化&quot;<br />\n有P2P想replace銀行，有網站app想replace地產中介<br />\n銀行就難replace，因佢除左做中介仲有好多作用同業務<br />\n地產agent作用就相對單一<br />\n個人認為地產agent會漸漸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"但二手樓賣家應該好需要AA"},{"pid":"7a80b8cd09e22bdcd60515c4a6cd31d089d4b1bb","tid":711303,"uid":166933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"p